INFO 2025-04-20 22:41:09,198 doc_processor 32 140324576328576 Generating title and summary for text: UNOFFICIALUNOFFICIALUNOFFICIALUNOFFICIALPROPOSAL TO AMEND CERTAIN PROVISIONS OF BOR RESOLUTION NO. 393 SERIES OF
2013 OF MSU-IIT

1.  Rationale

The Mindanao State University-Iligan Institute of Technology (MSU-IIT) is consistent in its
efforts  in  supporting  students  by  incentivizing  their  outstanding  academic  performance.  The
primordial objective of giving incentives is to recognize students’ achievement in the pursuit of
academic excellence. In the same vein,  the incentive is to augment  students’ cost of living by
providing  a  monthly  stipend  based  on  their  grade  point  average  (GPA).  Thus  it  was  on  this
premise that BOR Res No. 393, S. 2013 was approved known as The Unified MSU-IIT Internal
Scholarship.
