INFO 2025-04-21 07:09:15,052 documents 449 139646323328704 Chunks: [Document(id='doc_75_chunk_0', metadata={'id': 'doc_75_chunk_0', 'index': 0, 'doc_id': 75}, page_content='www.msuiit edu.ph\n\nOffice of the University Chancellor\nMindanao State University - Iligan Institute of Technology\n\nInfluencing the Future\n\nSPECIAL ORDER\nno. 008 09 -iit\nSeries of 2023\n\nMarch 28, 2023\n\nSUBJECT:\n\nConstitution of Working Committees for the University Palakasan 2023\n\nIn order to ensure the effective and successful conduct of the 2023 Palakasan on April\n\n22-26, 2023, committees are created, to be composed of the following:\n\nSTEERING COMMITTEE\n\nThe following personnel shall supervise the overall planning and conduct of the\ncommittees for submission to the\n\nPalakasan, and consolidate reports from all working\nManagement.\n\nChairperson:\nCo-Chairperson:\n\nRohane M. Derogongan\nPhyllis Marie S. Teanco\n\nMembers:'), Document(id='doc_75_chunk_1', metadata={'id': 'doc_75_chunk_1', 'index': 1, 'doc_id': 75}, page_content='Palakasan, and consolidate reports from all working\nManagement.\n\nChairperson:\nCo-Chairperson:\n\nRohane M. Derogongan\nPhyllis Marie S. Teanco\n\nMembers:\n\nRedeemtor R. Sacayan\nMary Grace M. Semine\nJay Rome O. Delos Santos\nMark Durog\nPeter D. Suson\nRabby Q. Lavilles\nLeo N. Santillana\nJay Roel Semilla\nRenebel 0. Labadisos\nAmado C. Guinto Jr.\nSuhaydah M. Saripada\nCarlo Stephen O. Moneva\nJoel I. Miano\nSittie Noffaisah B. Pasandalan\nJeinalisa Bayadog\n\nMichael Lloyd A. Bation\nRamel T Calo\nLoi Vincent C. Deriada\nCheryl C. Encabo\nHassanor S. Bansao\nJaypee S. Yongco\nJohn Gieveson E. Iglupas\nRambe C. Ramel, Jr.\nJed B. Otano\nKiziah G. Dato\nNoel R. Estoperez\nNieva M. Mapula\nAngelina P. Dinoro\nArt Brian Escabarte\nDaryl O. Porras\n\nStudent Representatives: Veanamari Elise V. Santillan\n\nJhune Ace Lubang\n\nSecretariat\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nChairperson:\nMembers:\n\nMary Grace M. Semine\nVai Syd rick Abarca\nNino Roel Balaba\nCris Enterone\n\nTasks:'), Document(id='doc_75_chunk_2', metadata={'id': 'doc_75_chunk_2', 'index': 2, 'doc_id': 75}, page_content='Jhune Ace Lubang\n\nSecretariat\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nChairperson:\nMembers:\n\nMary Grace M. Semine\nVai Syd rick Abarca\nNino Roel Balaba\nCris Enterone\n\nTasks:\n\n•  Coordinates with all Committees;\n•  Takes the minutes of Steering Committee meetings and reports the same at the start of\n\nsucceeding meetings; and\n\n•  Consolidates Committee reports and prepares the final report of the Steering Committee\n\nin coordination with the Documentation Committee.\n\nTelefax: (063) 221-4056 (DL)\nchancellor@g. msuiit.edu.ph\n\nAndres Bonifacio Avenue,\nTibanga, Iligan City, 9200 aJ\n\n\x0cwww.msuiit.edu.ph\n\nOffice of the University Chancellor\nMindanao State University - Iligan Institute of Technology\n\nInfluencing the Future\n\nBudget and Finance Committee\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nChairperson:\nCo-Chairperson:\nMembers:\n\nMichael Lloyd A. Bati-on\nCathlene Funny Apresto\nYenusha Faye Lusica\nMary Gracelin Bacarizas\nJean Antoinette Cortes\nChristnel Ceballos'), Document(id='doc_75_chunk_3', metadata={'id': 'doc_75_chunk_3', 'index': 3, 'doc_id': 75}, page_content='Michael Lloyd A. Bati-on\nCathlene Funny Apresto\nYenusha Faye Lusica\nMary Gracelin Bacarizas\nJean Antoinette Cortes\nChristnel Ceballos\n\nProcurement Committee\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nChairperson:\nCo-Chairperson:\n\nJeinalisa Bayadog\nYenusha Faye Lusica\nCathlene Funny Apresto\n\nTasks:\n\n•  Take charge of all the financial operating activities, procedures, controls, and\n\ndisbursements in relation of the event\n\n•  Take charge the budget formulation and preparation\n•  Take charge of procuring the lights and sound equipment.\n•  Submits the financial report of expenses to the Steering Committee.\n\nLogistics, Physical Arrangement and Decoration of Gymnasium Committee\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nChairperson:\nCo-Chairperson:\n\nRamel T. Calo\nNino Roel Balaba\nRayed Laguindab Sani\nThea Cabrera\nRiamie Villar Dalumbar\nKristel Bliss Romano\nGabriel Vincent Mercado\nAina Tutong\n\nLevi lanu\nLugille Castardo\nRaima Amerol\nAngeli Danielle Manseras\nLady Lyn A. Tagalogon\n\nMembers:\n\nTasks:'), Document(id='doc_75_chunk_4', metadata={'id': 'doc_75_chunk_4', 'index': 4, 'doc_id': 75}, page_content='Levi lanu\nLugille Castardo\nRaima Amerol\nAngeli Danielle Manseras\nLady Lyn A. Tagalogon\n\nMembers:\n\nTasks:\n\n•  Ensures availability of the gymnasium and other venues for all PALAKASAN-related\n\nactivities;\n\n•  Prepares the over-all logistical plan such as the location of the contests,\n\nsponsorships/donors, activity partners etc.\n\n•  Handles the request of the tables and chairs to be used\n•  Facilitates in the hanging of streamers & tarpaulins\n•  Set-up and retrieve all physical/logistical requirements of each committee\n•  Prepares and plans stage background and decoration\n•  Coordinates with the secretariat and Event chairman in relation to the venue /location of\n\nthe event\n\nDocumentation Committee\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nChairperson:\nCo-Chairperson:\nMembers:\n\nJay Rome O. Delos Santos\nCollin Superales\nA Espina\nXander Cage Raman\nSon Reil Ragot\nRed Nichole Pacoy\nAlexa Jillian Reyes Castillon\n\nSaira Andrea Melegrito\nShakira Farhana Derico\nQueenie Joy Cabatingan'), Document(id='doc_75_chunk_5', metadata={'id': 'doc_75_chunk_5', 'index': 5, 'doc_id': 75}, page_content='Saira Andrea Melegrito\nShakira Farhana Derico\nQueenie Joy Cabatingan\n\nTelefax: (063) 221-4056 (DL)\nchancellor@g.msuiit.edu.ph\n\nAndres Bonifacio Avenue,\nTibanga, Iligan City, 9200\n\n\x0cwww.msuiit.edu.ph\n\nTasks:\n\nOffice of the University Chancellor\nMindanao State University - Iligan Institute of Technology\n\nInfluencing the Future\n\n•  Takes charge of the documentation (i.e., photos, video, etc.) of all pre-event and during\n\nPALAKASAN activities\n\n•  Assigns accredited photographers for the PALAKASAN activities;\n\n•  Ensures that all accredited photographers are easily identifiable during the PALAKASAN\n\nactivities by wearing black outfit;\n\n•  Ensures that an evaluation of the PALAKASAN activities are conducted and submits a\n\nreport on the evaluation.\n\nPublication, Social Media, and Press Information Committee\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nChairperson:\n\nLoi Vincent C. Deriada\nPamela II Pepito\n\nCo-Chairperson:\n\nMembers:\n\nTasks:\n\nJarl Caesar Ymanuel Epanto'), Document(id='doc_75_chunk_6', metadata={'id': 'doc_75_chunk_6', 'index': 6, 'doc_id': 75}, page_content='Loi Vincent C. Deriada\nPamela II Pepito\n\nCo-Chairperson:\n\nMembers:\n\nTasks:\n\nJarl Caesar Ymanuel Epanto\n\nMichael Anthony Vallejo\nLydie Carylle Leyes\nCatherine BadiHa\nSaadodin Pendatun Jr.\nVan Carlo Labanan\nXander Cage Paman\n\nToni Gorgolon\nCrystal Weisz De Guzman\nJonathan Israel Gelogo\nJohaymen Malawani\n\n•  Promote student activities as required by each committee through social networks,\n\nposting, other means of promotion/ information dissemination\n\n•  Design the poster, streamer, and tarpaulin\n•  Establish and maintains linkages with the outside community in matters relevant to the\n\n•\n\ninformation dissemination/promotion documentation\nIn charge of answering messages and inquiries regarding the KASAMA Social Media\nAccounts\n\n•  Release Official Statements of KASAMA on relevant issues and FAQs\n•  Ensure activities are posted on the KASAMA Social Media Accounts\n•  Ensure that the posts of KASAMA in all social media accounts attain maximum reach.\n\nGrievance and Complaints Committee'), Document(id='doc_75_chunk_7', metadata={'id': 'doc_75_chunk_7', 'index': 7, 'doc_id': 75}, page_content='Grievance and Complaints Committee\n\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nChairperson:\nCo-Chairperson:\nMembers:\n\nRedeemtor Sacayan\nKyle Christian Tuquib\nChristine Joy Amper\nShernan Franz Samson\nGlecie Mae Panes\n\nTasks:\n\n•  Responsible for resolving matters relating to conflicts, complaints, and/ or grievance of\nevent matters and/ or officer/s and/ or members of the committee against a participant as\nmaybe referred from time to time\nImplement written policies related to resolving conflicts/complaints\n\n•\n\nTabulation and Results\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nChairperson:\n\nMark Durog\nAlliah Fayesha Elcamil\n\nTelefax: (063) 221-4056 (DL)\nchancellor@g.msuiit.edu.ph\n\nAndres Bonifacio Avenue,\nTibanga, Iligan City, 9200\n\n\x0cwww.msuiit.edu.ph\n\nCo-Chairperson:\nMembers:\n\nOffice of the University Chancellor\nMindanao State University - Iligan Institute of Technology\n\nInfluencing the Future'), Document(id='doc_75_chunk_8', metadata={'id': 'doc_75_chunk_8', 'index': 8, 'doc_id': 75}, page_content='www.msuiit.edu.ph\n\nCo-Chairperson:\nMembers:\n\nOffice of the University Chancellor\nMindanao State University - Iligan Institute of Technology\n\nInfluencing the Future\n\nThea Cabrera\nMohammad Raid Sani\nLugille Marien Castardo\nCredenda Valerie Baja\nChristille Shyra Norbe\nGerald Karl Avila\nCenterelle Salvaha\nMark Ryan L. Uy\nReylen Oracion\nSarah Jane Nava\n\nErin Joyce Paluga\nNicole Asuncion D. Ancheta\nJoshua Venzon\n\nMavelle Dorothy Serate\n\nRhea Rachel Canoneo\nRahmah Naga Azis\nAlexander Jules Barrete\nPaulinne Thiesha Baloro\nFaith Ashley Alidon\n\nTasks:\n\n•  Responsible for collection of all the results sheets from the judges after each event\n•  Observe confidentiality\n•  Manage all tabulation related systems during the entire Palakasan\n•  Responsible for all tabulation committee related tasks.\n\nFood Committee\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nChairperson:\nCo-Chairperson:\nMembers:\n\nTask:\n\nCheryl C. Encabo\nKimberly Lopez\nMary Twinxer Nuevas\nHernan Garcia\nMitchelyn Loresco\n\nKeith David Ramayla'), Document(id='doc_75_chunk_9', metadata={'id': 'doc_75_chunk_9', 'index': 9, 'doc_id': 75}, page_content='Food Committee\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nChairperson:\nCo-Chairperson:\nMembers:\n\nTask:\n\nCheryl C. Encabo\nKimberly Lopez\nMary Twinxer Nuevas\nHernan Garcia\nMitchelyn Loresco\n\nKeith David Ramayla\n\n• Coordinates with appropriate Committees regarding preparation and distribution of\n\nsnacks and meals for the working committee, judges and sports officials.\n\nWays and Means\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nChairperson:\nCo-Chairperson:\nMembers:\n\nSuhaydah M. Saripada\nAries Espina\nMa. Arvie Faith Escasinas\nMicah Real\nMa. Arvie Joyce Escasinas\nShane Marie Villoria\nHermione Sansona\nMary Gwyneth Manlapaz\n\nShania Gonzaga\nNathaniel Palma\nNaim Saad\nJohn Paul Villamora\n\nTask:\n\n• In charge of finding donors, sponsorships, solicitations, and any means that would\n\ndefray the operational expenses of the whole duration of the event\n\nHealth, Safety Management Services & Security and Order Committee\nFaculty/Staff Coordinators: Peter D. Suson & Hassanor S. Bansao\nChairperson:\nCo-Chairperson:\nMembers:'), Document(id='doc_75_chunk_10', metadata={'id': 'doc_75_chunk_10', 'index': 10, 'doc_id': 75}, page_content='Health, Safety Management Services & Security and Order Committee\nFaculty/Staff Coordinators: Peter D. Suson & Hassanor S. Bansao\nChairperson:\nCo-Chairperson:\nMembers:\n\nVeanamari Elise Santillan\nHernan Garcia\nAlyssa T. Heyrana\nMariane Therese Ambag\n\nRecca Marie Azarcon\n\nTasks:\n\n•  Responsible for the overall direction of all security functions\n•  Observe and report any unlawful or inappropriate activity\n\nTelefax: (063) 221-4056 (DL)\nchancellor@g.msuiit.edu.ph\n\nAndres Bonifacio Avenue,\nTibanga, Iligan City, 9200\n\n\x0cwww msuiit edu.ph\n\nOffice of the University Chancellor\nMindanao State University - Iligan Institute of Technology\n\nInfluencing the Future\n\n•  Provide protection and ensure safety for Individuals and property\n•  Manage emergency situations and report to authorities as appropriate\n•  Ensures that the University’s medical staff and rescue team are prepared to respond to\n\nemergencies during all pre-event and during PALAKASAN activities;'), Document(id='doc_75_chunk_11', metadata={'id': 'doc_75_chunk_11', 'index': 11, 'doc_id': 75}, page_content='emergencies during all pre-event and during PALAKASAN activities;\n\n•  Assigns medical personnel at the venues for all pre-event and during PALAKASAN\n\nactivities;\n\n•  Ensures that medical kits are available;\n•  Assigns medical personnel at the clinic during all pre-event and during PALAKASAN\n\nactivities; and\n\n•  To quickly and effectively respond to and recover from disaster\n\nPlanning and Stage Production Management & Audio and Multimedia System\n(Technicals) Committee\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nChairperson:\nCo-Chairperson:\nMembers:\n\nRabby Q. Lavilles\nKrisha Jane D. Intay\nChester Laurie Tagacay\nLouie Ayade\nChristine Ombrete\nKryzzl Joie R. Lastimosa\n\nTasks:\n\n•  This Committee shall be in-charge of securing the production, blockings, practices,\n\npreparation, schedules, and oversee the whole event production.\n\n•  Collect and arrange the schedules of every event committee Contest, Judging, Activities,\n\nWorkshops, Blockings, Rehearsals, and Schedules'), Document(id='doc_75_chunk_12', metadata={'id': 'doc_75_chunk_12', 'index': 12, 'doc_id': 75}, page_content='•  Collect and arrange the schedules of every event committee Contest, Judging, Activities,\n\nWorkshops, Blockings, Rehearsals, and Schedules\n\nLIST OF OUTSTANDING AND AD HOC COMMITTEES\n\nCommittee for Opening Day & Closing Day\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nFaculty Asst Coordinator:\nChairperson:\nCo-Chairperson:\n\nJaypee S. Yongco\nElmar Albios\nAdjemore A. Manabat\nChristine Tecson\n\nCommittee for Sports Events:\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nChairperson:\nCo-Chairperson:\nMembers:\n\nLeo N. Santillana\nQueenie Mae Gabisay\nJackielyn Marie Cartin\nJustin Ray Heredia\nKyle Cresta Leong\nWishka Almerol\n\nColleen Kristine Suerte\nLowell Vicente\n\nCommittee for Badminton Tournament:\nFaculty/Staff Chairperson:\nFacult