rly Bonete\nFatima Myrrh\nHoly Faith Opog\n\nRochelle Rose Rocha\nKrizyl Ann Ong\nJhon Lloyd Pioquinto\n\nCommittee for Special Events\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator: Jed B. Otano\nFaculty/Staff Co-coordinator: John Leandro Reyes\nChairperson:\nCo-Chairperson:\nMembers:\n\nCherry Mae Tabaha\nAlfrem Mogan & Kryzzl Joie Lastimosa\nKecy Naneth Saliwa\nCharles Frederick Tilacas\nCris Enterone\n\nFrancis Vale\nMe PG II Abayan\n\nCommittee for Mx. Influencer\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nChairperson:\n\nCo-Chairperson:\nMembers:'), Document(id='doc_75_chunk_17', metadata={'id': 'doc_75_chunk_17', 'index': 17, 'doc_id': 75}, page_content='Francis Vale\nMe PG II Abayan\n\nCommittee for Mx. Influencer\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nChairperson:\n\nCo-Chairperson:\nMembers:\n\nAmado C. Guinto Jr.\nChristine Jane Tecson\nAndrianne Nicole Arda\nMeggie Denise Villanueva\nMary Grace Cabalhin\nBeatrix Julianna Marie Malacas\nCedric Pejan\nLynne Jasel Mutia\n\nIrene Canete\nErnest Sabilla\nJanrose Sabuero\nEN Khrisna Carumba\nShekirah Maghinay\n\nProduction Team:\nCreatives Team:\n\nHeaded by Trixcel Emborong of Trixavaganga\nThe Tent Studio\n\nCommittee for MSU-IIT Drag Superstar\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nChairperson:\nCo-Chairperson:\nMembers:\n\nDaryl O. Porras & Jaypee S. Yongco\nAlfrem Mogan\nIan Zandro\nNikko Shane Dar\n\nHujaype Lomondot\nShaina Joy Aban\nMil Opema Agan\nSheindyl Ann Jabines\n\nAnthony Gerarman\nChristfer-John Maglasang\nVerneece Charity Amlon\nJoanna Rose Alo\nDominador Mayion Jr.\n\nCommittee for Awards, Prizes, Tokens, and Certificates\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nChairperson:\nCo-Chairperson:'), Document(id='doc_75_chunk_18', metadata={'id': 'doc_75_chunk_18', 'index': 18, 'doc_id': 75}, page_content='Committee for Awards, Prizes, Tokens, and Certificates\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nChairperson:\nCo-Chairperson:\n\nKiziah G. Dato\nSheika Shaila Aclainie G. Bacolod\nHyrah Kaye C. Hallera & Hafzah Imam\n\nCommittee for Lights & Sound, Power, and Ventilation\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nChairperson:\nCo-Chairperson:\n\nNoel R. Estoperez\nCris Enterone\nVai Sydrick Abarca\n\nTelefax: (063) 221-4056 (DL)\nchancellor@g.msuiit.edu.ph\n\nAndres Bonifacio Avenue,\nTlbanga, Iligan City, 9200\n\n\x0cwww.msuiit.edu.ph\n\nOffice of the University Chancellor\nMindanao State University - Iligan Institute of Technology\n\nInfluencing the Future\n\nAll committees shall perform other tasks as may be assigned by the overall Chairperson\nof the activity. The chairperson of each committee shall submit a report to the Steering\nCommittee for consolidation.'), Document(id='doc_75_chunk_19', metadata={'id': 'doc_75_chunk_19', 'index': 19, 'doc_id': 75}, page_content='In support of this activity, all students shall be excused from their classes during the\nperiod stipulated above. They shall also be allowed entry to the campus during weekends and\nholidays for rehearsals (until 8:00 p.m.) only, subject to University policies and regulations.\nFurther, the students shall be allowed the use of available University facilities, free of charge, for\nthe 2023 Palakasan.\n\nIn addition, preliminary games for the Palakasan (Sports and eSports) shall be\n\nconducted on March 27, 2023.\n\nAll expenses pertaining to the conduct of the Palakasan shall be charged against the\nbudget allocated for the 2023 Palakasan, subject to existing accounting and auditing rules and\nregulations.\n\nOvertime fees for janitorial services and technical support shall be provided for services\nrendered during the duration of the activities, charged against the approved budget allocation\nfor 2023 Palakasan, subject to the usual accounting and auditing rules and regulations.'), Document(id='doc_75_chunk_20', metadata={'id': 'doc_75_chunk_20', 'index': 20, 'doc_id': 75}, page_content='This Order is effective on the period stipulated above, unless revoked by competent\n\nauthority.\n\nALIZJ\nChancellor\n\nEY M. DITUCALAI\n\nTelefax: (063) 221-4056 (DL)\nchancellor@g.msuiit.edu. ph\n\nAndres Bonifacio Avenue, .\nTibanga, Iligan City, 9200')]
