mittee\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nChairperson:\nCo-Chairperson:\nMembers:\n\nAsst. Prof. Cheryl C. Encabo\nJustin Ray Heredia\nCharlie Vanguardia\nMitchelyn Loresco\nCrizza Sialana\nRovic A. Daligdig\nJohn Kenneth Setiar\nRobert A. Amaquin\nJoshua M. Estoque\nViadimer A. Labandero\nChris Cyril B. Fernandez\nMiguel Rhoi B. Sumaylo\nViel P. Cero\nKarl Andre A. Babanto\nStacy Lee D. Gaerian\n\nTask:\n\n• Coordinates with the appropriate committees regarding the preparation and distribution\n\nof snacks and meals for the working committee, judges, and sports officials.'), Document(id='doc_74_chunk_6', metadata={'id': 'doc_74_chunk_6', 'index': 6, 'doc_id': 74}, page_content='Task:\n\n• Coordinates with the appropriate committees regarding the preparation and distribution\n\nof snacks and meals for the working committee, judges, and sports officials.\n\nWays and Means\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nChairperson:\nCo-Chairperson:\nMembers:\n\nAsst. Prof. Cheryl C. Encabo\nKrizyl Ann E. Ong\nWilson Sembrano Jr.\nLieka Disocor Tawano\nJune Leonard Mingo\nRodolfo II E. Cuadra\nNina Balangue\nJevan Dela Cruz\nJan Missy A. Arriesgado\n\nTask:\n\n• In-Charge of finding donors, sponsorships, solicitations, and any means that would\n\ndefray the operational expenses for the whole duration of the event and conduct the sale\nof Palakasan merch and tabo.\n\nMSU - III Incident Command System\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nChairperson:\n\nJaypee S. Yungco\nChester Laurie C. Tagacay\n\nTasks:'), Document(id='doc_74_chunk_7', metadata={'id': 'doc_74_chunk_7', 'index': 7, 'doc_id': 74}, page_content='MSU - III Incident Command System\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nChairperson:\n\nJaypee S. Yungco\nChester Laurie C. Tagacay\n\nTasks:\n\n•  Responsible for the overall direction of all security functions.\n•  Observe and report any unlawful or inappropriate activity.\n•  Provide protection and ensure safety for individuals and property.\n•  Manage emergencies and report to authorities as appropriate.\n\nTelefax: (063) 221-4056 (DL)\nchancellor@g msuiit.edu.ph\n\nAndres Bonifacio Avenue,\nTibanga, Iligan City, 9200^/\n\n\x0cwww.msuiit.edu.ph\n\nOffice of the University Chancellor\nMindanao State University ■ Iligan Institute of Technology\n\nInfluencing the Future\n\n•  Ensures that the universities’ medical staff and rescue team are prepared to respond to\n\nemergencies during all pre-event and during PALAKASAN activities;\n\n•  Assigns medical personnel at the venues for all pre-event and during PALAKASAN\n\nactivities;'), Document(id='doc_74_chunk_8', metadata={'id': 'doc_74_chunk_8', 'index': 8, 'doc_id': 74}, page_content='emergencies during all pre-event and during PALAKASAN activities;\n\n•  Assigns medical personnel at the venues for all pre-event and during PALAKASAN\n\nactivities;\n\n•  Ensures that medical kits are available;\n•  Assign medical personnel at the clinic during all pre-event and during PALAKASAN\n\nactivities; and\n\n•  To quickly and effectively respond to and recover from disaster\n\nPlanning and Stage Production Management & Audio and Multimedia System\n(Technicals) Committee\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nChairperson:\nCo-Chairperson:\nMembers:\n\nFitz Gerald Torralba\nLanna Mae Balaba\nVaughn Nagba\nClarkent Potestas\nJohn Joshua Barcenal\nJar Jr. I. Rosales\nCharisse Sard\n\nTasks:\n\n•  This Committee shall be in charge of securing the production, blockings, practices,\n\npreparation, schedules, and oversee the whole event production.\n\n•  Collect and arrange the schedules of every event committee Contest, Judging, Activities,\n\nWorkshops, Blockings, Rehearsals, Schedules'), Document(id='doc_74_chunk_9', metadata={'id': 'doc_74_chunk_9', 'index': 9, 'doc_id': 74}, page_content='•  Collect and arrange the schedules of every event committee Contest, Judging, Activities,\n\nWorkshops, Blockings, Rehearsals, Schedules\n\nLIST OF OUTSTANDING AND AD HOC COMMITTEES\n\nCommittee for Opening Day & Closing Day\nChairperson:\nCo-Chairperson:\n\nHannah Polangi\nChester Laurie C. Tagacay\n\nCommittee for Sports Events:\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nChairperson:\nCo-Chairperson:\nMembers:\n\nCommittee for Literary Events\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nFaculty/Staff Asst. Coordinator:\nChairperson:\nCo-Chairperson:\nMembers:\n\nLeo N. Santillana\nAlfrem Mogan\nLowell Vicente\nApril Wency Tugahan\nRobb Thomas Adonis\nReygie Ajosan\nKristine Suerte\nSally Pacalna\n\nKassandra A. Buenafe\nAdjemore A. Manabat\nAriel II Ebale\nSarah Jane M. Navia\nArjie P. Castillon\nCeline Margareth F. Wee\nAl A. Lial\nAngela Valderama\nGiuelle Faith Dagulo\n\nTelefax: (063) 221-4056 (DL)\nchancellor@g.msuiit.edu.ph\n\nAndres Bonifacio Avenue,\nTibanga, Iligan City, 9200^\n\n\x0cwww.msuiit.edu.ph'), Document(id='doc_74_chunk_10', metadata={'id': 'doc_74_chunk_10', 'index': 10, 'doc_id': 74}, page_content='Telefax: (063) 221-4056 (DL)\nchancellor@g.msuiit.edu.ph\n\nAndres Bonifacio Avenue,\nTibanga, Iligan City, 9200^\n\n\x0cwww.msuiit.edu.ph\n\nOffice of the University Chancellor\nMindanao State University - Iligan Institute of Technology\n\nInfluencing the Future\n\nCommittee for Chancellor’s Cup: Debate Tournament\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nChairperson:\n\nPhyllis Marie S. Teanco\nArt Joseph Tarranza\n\nCommittee for Culture and Arts & Nights of Festivities (Dances and Songs)\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nChairperson:\nCo-Chairperson:\nMembers:\n\nAsst. Prof. Amado Guinto Jr\nHermione Sheevey Sansona\nMarvin Puno\nWellah Lindy Rabilas\nFatima Myrrh Carpentero\nConnie Harriette Velarde\n\nCommittee for Special Events\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nCo- Adviser:\nChairperson:\nCo-Chairperson:\n\nCommittee for Mx. Influencer\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nChairperson:\nCo-Chairperson:\nMembers:\n\nProduction Team:\nCreatives Team:\n\nCommittee for Wannabe\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nChairperson:'), Document(id='doc_74_chunk_11', metadata={'id': 'doc_74_chunk_11', 'index': 11, 'doc_id': 74}, page_content='Committee for Mx. Influencer\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nChairperson:\nCo-Chairperson:\nMembers:\n\nProduction Team:\nCreatives Team:\n\nCommittee for Wannabe\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nChairperson:\n\nCommittee for Street Dance\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nChairperson:\n\nCommittee for Film Festival\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nChairperson:\nCo-Chairperson:\nMembers:\n\nJed Otano\nTilshane R.Yap\nShakira Farhana Derico\nJonh Paul Villamora\n\nJohn Leandro Reyes\nMary Grace C. Cabalhin\nEN Khrisna B. Carumba\nAngel Mae S. Manon-og\nCarl Mark Dela Cruz\nBarbara Marie Tan\nVaughn Carlo Nagba\n\nTrixcel Jan Ruiz Emborong\nAlex & B studio\nAce Films PH\n\nJed Otano\nMeg Nathalie Nobleza\n\nJed Otano\nAbdul Haleem Racmat\n\nIan Embradura\nFrankie James Balos\nDave Daniel Cardino\nTristan Jadman\nBarby Gwynne Ebardo\nLemuel Matthew Elumba\n\nCommittee for Awards, Prizes, Tokens, and Certificates\nKiziah G. Dato\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nWishka Almerol\nChairperson:\n\nTelefax: (063) 221-4056 (DL)\nchancellor@g.msuiit.edu.ph'), Document(id='doc_74_chunk_12', metadata={'id': 'doc_74_chunk_12', 'index': 12, 'doc_id': 74}, page_content='Committee for Awards, Prizes, Tokens, and Certificates\nKiziah G. Dato\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator:\nWishka Almerol\nChairperson:\n\nTelefax: (063) 221-4056 (DL)\nchancellor@g.msuiit.edu.ph\n\nAndres Bonifacio Avenue.\nTibanga. Iligan City. 9200^/\n\n\x0cwww.msuiit.edu.ph\n\nOffice of the University Chancellor\nMindanao State University - Iligan Institute of Technology\n\nInfluencing the Future\n\nMember:\n\nWilliam Joseph Otero\n\nAll committees shall perform other tasks as may be assigned by the overall Chairperson\nof the activity. The chairperson of each committee shall submit a report to the Steering\nCommittee for consolidation.\n\nAs such, the KASAMA shall be granted the following:\n\n1.  Suspend the classes and other academic activities (to wit: clinical duties, on-the-job\ntraining, practice teaching, etc.) on April 26-30, 2024. April 26, 2024 is the grand\nrehearsal day for all the colleges for their final preparations;'), Document(id='doc_74_chunk_13', metadata={'id': 'doc_74_chunk_13', 'index': 13, 'doc_id': 74}, page_content='2.  Excuse the KASAMA officers and working committees from their work and classes on\nApril 25, 2024 for the final preparations of Palakasan 2024. In addition, certain students\nwho are joining workshops shall also be excused from their classes. The students shall\nmake up for missed academic activities;\n\n3.  Use of University facilities, free of charge, namely: Gymnasium, Mini Theater, Sports\n\nFacilities in the campus, and other available venue neede for the Palakasan 2024;\n\n4.  Use of Gymnasium in April 26-30, 2024 (1:00 p.m. - 9:00 p.m.);\n5.  Utilize the funds allocated for Palaksan 2024, subject to approved line-item-budget and\n\nstandard accounting and auditing procedures;\n\n6.  Allow students to enter the campus on weekends and holidays (until 9:00 p.m.), subject\n\nto University protocols;\n\n7.  Allow the conduct of training for the sports events at the Gymnasium, Twin Court, IDS\n\nMPH on March 11-26, 2024 (until 9:00 p.m.);'), Document(id='doc_74_chunk_14', metadata={'id': 'doc_74_chunk_14', 'index': 14, 'doc_id': 74}, page_content='to University protocols;\n\n7.  Allow the conduct of training for the sports events at the Gymnasium, Twin Court, IDS\n\nMPH on March 11-26, 2024 (until 9:00 p.m.);\n\n8.  Seek the services of the Clinic Personnel and Mindanao Center for Resiliency on April\n27-28, 2024 and May 1, 2024 during the conduct of the activities. Expenses incurred in\nduring this period are charged against University funds;\n\n9.  Render overtime services for certain personnel; fees for the services rendered, if\n\napplicable, are charged against KASAMA and OVCSS funds;\n\n10. Use of available University vehicles to ferry students after the Night Events, from\n\nMSU-IIT to an agreed common destination or their residences;\n\n11.  Conduct preliminar and off-campus activities (to wit: workshops, closed-door interviews,\noutreach program, and press launching), subject to University and other applicable\npolicies regarding student participation in off-campus activities; and'), Document(id='doc_74_chunk_15', metadata={'id': 'doc_74_chunk_15', 'index': 15, 'doc_id': 74}, page_content='12. Allow KASAMA to conduct Palakasan Trade Fair at the Rizal Park on April 23-30, 2024,\n\nsubject to the approval of the Director of OBA.\n\nAll expenses are charged against the approved budget allocation for 2024 Palakasan,\n\nsubject to the usual accounting and auditing rules and regulations.\n\nThis Order is effective on the dates stipulated above, unless revoked by competent\n\nauthority.\n\nAJJZEDNEY M. DI\nChancellor\n\nALAN\n\nTelefax: (063) 221-4056 (DL)\nchancellor@g msuiit.edu.ph\n\nAndres Bonifacio Avenue.\nTibanga, Iligan City. 9200^')]
