INFO 2025-04-21 07:28:19,045 documents 449 139646314936000 Chunks: [Document(id='doc_78_chunk_0', metadata={'id': 'doc_78_chunk_0', 'index': 0, 'doc_id': 78}, page_content='Influencing the Future\n\nMarch 28, 2023\n\nSPECIAL ORDER no. 008 09 -iit Series of 2023\n\n#### SUBJECT: **Constitution of Working Committees for the University Palakasan 2023**\n\nIn order to ensure the effective and successful conduct of the 2023 Palakasan on April 22-26, 2023, committees are created, to be composed of the following:\n\n### **STEERING COMMITTEE**\n\ncommittees for submission to the The following personnel shall supervise the overall planning and conduct of the Palakasan, and consolidate reports from all working Management.'), Document(id='doc_78_chunk_1', metadata={'id': 'doc_78_chunk_1', 'index': 1, 'doc_id': 78}, page_content='| Chairperson:<br>Co-Chairperson:                                       | Rohane M. Derogongan<br>Phyllis Marie S. Teanco                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |'), Document(id='doc_78_chunk_2', metadata={'id': 'doc_78_chunk_2', 'index': 2, 'doc_id': 78}, page_content='|-----------------------------------------------------------------------|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|'), Document(id='doc_78_chunk_3', metadata={'id': 'doc_78_chunk_3', 'index': 3, 'doc_id': 78}, page_content='| Members:                                                              | Redeemtor R. Sacayan<br>Mary Grace M. Semine<br>Jay Rome O. Delos Santos<br>Mark Durog<br>Peter D. Suson<br>Rabby Q. Lavilles<br>Leo N. Santillana<br>Jay Roel Semilla<br>Renebel 0.<br>Labadisos<br>Amado C. Guinto Jr.<br>Suhaydah M. Saripada<br>Carlo Stephen O. Moneva<br>Joel I. Miano<br>Sittie Noffaisah B. Pasandalan<br>Jeinalisa Bayadog | Michael Lloyd A. Bation<br>Ramel T<br>Calo<br>Loi Vincent C. Deriada<br>Cheryl C. Encabo<br>Hassanor S. Bansao<br>Jaypee S. Yongco<br>John Gieveson E. Iglupas<br>Rambe C. Ramel, Jr.<br>Jed B. Otano<br>Kiziah G. Dato<br>Noel R. Estoperez<br>Nieva M. Mapula<br>Angelina P. Dinoro<br>Art Brian Escabarte<br>Daryl O. Porras |'), Document(id='doc_78_chunk_4', metadata={'id': 'doc_78_chunk_4', 'index': 4, 'doc_id': 78}, page_content='| Student Representatives:                                              | Veanamari Elise V. Santillan                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        | Jhune Ace Lubang                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |'), Document(id='doc_78_chunk_5', metadata={'id': 'doc_78_chunk_5', 'index': 5, 'doc_id': 78}, page_content='| Secretariat<br>Faculty/Staff Coordinator:<br>Chairperson:<br>Members: | Mary Grace M. Semine<br>Vai Sydrick Abarca<br>Nino Roel Balaba<br>Cris Enterone                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |'), Document(id='doc_78_chunk_6', metadata={'id': 'doc_78_chunk_6', 'index': 6, 'doc_id': 78}, page_content='Tasks:\n\n- Coordinates with all Committees;\n- Takes the minutes of Steering Committee meetings and reports the same at the start of succeeding meetings; and\n- Consolidates Committee reports and prepares the final report of the Steering Committee in coordination with the Documentation Committee.\n\nInfluencing the Future\n\n## **Budget and Finance Committee**\n\n| Faculty/Staff Coordinator: | Michael Lloyd A. Bati-on |\n|----------------------------|--------------------------|\n| Chairperson:               | Cathlene Funny Apresto   |\n| Co-Chairperson:            | Yenusha Faye Lusica      |\n| Members:                   | Mary Gracelin Bacarizas  |\n|                            | Jean Antoinette Cortes   |\n|                            |                          |\n\n### **Procurement Committee**\n\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator: Chairperson: Co-Chairperson:\n\nYenusha Faye Lusica Mary Gracelin Bacarizas Jean Antoinette Cortes Christnel Ceballos'), Document(id='doc_78_chunk_7', metadata={'id': 'doc_78_chunk_7', 'index': 7, 'doc_id': 78}, page_content='### **Procurement Committee**\n\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator: Chairperson: Co-Chairperson:\n\nYenusha Faye Lusica Mary Gracelin Bacarizas Jean Antoinette Cortes Christnel Ceballos\n\nJeinalisa Bayadog Yenusha Faye Lusica Cathlene Funny Apresto\n\n### Tasks:\n\n- Take charge of all the financial operating activities, procedures, controls, and disbursements in relation of the event\n- Take charge the budget formulation and preparation\n- Take charge of procuring the lights and sound equipment.\n- Submits the financial report of expenses to the Steering Committee.\n\n## **Logistics, Physical Arrangement and Decoration of Gymnasium Committee**'), Document(id='doc_78_chunk_8', metadata={'id': 'doc_78_chunk_8', 'index': 8, 'doc_id': 78}, page_content='## **Logistics, Physical Arrangement and Decoration of Gymnasium Committee**\n\n| Faculty/Staff Coordinator: | Ramel T. Calo           |\n|----------------------------|-------------------------|\n| Chairperson:               | Nino Roel Balaba        |\n| Co-Chairperson:            | Rayed Laguindab Sani    |\n| Members:                   | Thea Cabrera            |\n|                            | Riamie Villar Dalumbar  |\n|                            | Kristel Bliss Romano    |\n|                            | Gabriel Vincent Mercado |\n|                            | Aina Tutong             |\n\nLevi lanu Lugille Castardo Raima Amerol Angeli Danielle Manseras Lady Lyn A. Tagalogon\n\n## Tasks:'), Document(id='doc_78_chunk_9', metadata={'id': 'doc_78_chunk_9', 'index': 9, 'doc_id': 78}, page_content='Levi lanu Lugille Castardo Raima Amerol Angeli Danielle Manseras Lady Lyn A. Tagalogon\n\n## Tasks:\n\n- Ensures availability of the gymnasium and other venues for all PALAKASAN-related activities;\n- Prepares the over-all logistical plan such as the location of the contests, sponsorships/donors, activity partners etc.\n- Handles the request of the tables and chairs to be used\n- Facilitates in the hanging of streamers & tarpaulins\n- Set-up and retrieve all physical/logistical requirements of each committee\n\nAlexa Jillian Reyes Castillon\n\n- Prepares and plans stage background and decoration\n- Coordinates with the secretariat and Event chairman in relation to the venue /location of the event\n\n## **Documentation Committee**'), Document(id='doc_78_chunk_10', metadata={'id': 'doc_78_chunk_10', 'index': 10, 'doc_id': 78}, page_content='- Prepares and plans stage background and decoration\n- Coordinates with the secretariat and Event chairman in relation to the venue /location of the event\n\n## **Documentation Committee**\n\n| Faculty/Staff Coordinator: | Jay Rome O. Delos Santos |  |\n|----------------------------|--------------------------|--|\n| Chairperson:               | Collin Superales         |  |\n| Co-Chairperson:            | A Espina                 |  |\n| Members:                   | Xander Cage Raman        |  |\n|                            | Son Reil Ragot           |  |\n|                            | Red Nichole Pacoy        |  |\n\nSaira Andrea Melegrito Shakira Farhana Derico Queenie Joy Cabatingan\n\n[www.msuiit.edu.ph](http://www.msuiit.edu.ph)\n\nTasks:'), Document(id='doc_78_chunk_11', metadata={'id': 'doc_78_chunk_11', 'index': 11, 'doc_id': 78}, page_content='Saira Andrea Melegrito Shakira Farhana Derico Queenie Joy Cabatingan\n\n[www.msuiit.edu.ph](http://www.msuiit.edu.ph)\n\nTasks:\n\n- Takes charge of the documentation (i.e., photos, video, etc.) of all pre-event and during PALAKASAN activities\n- Assigns accredited photographers for the PALAKASAN activities;\n- Ensures that all accredited photographers are easily identifiable during the PALAKASAN activities by wearing black outfit;\n- Ensures that an evaluation of the PALAKASAN activities are conducted and submits <sup>a</sup> report on the evaluation.\n\n# **Publication, Social Media, and Press Information Committee**'), Document(id='doc_78_chunk_12', metadata={'id': 'doc_78_chunk_12', 'index': 12, 'doc_id': 78}, page_content='| Faculty/Staff Coordinator: | Loi Vincent C. Deriada     |                         |\n|----------------------------|----------------------------|-------------------------|\n| Chairperson:               | Pamela II Pepito           |                         |\n| Co-Chairperson:            | Jarl Caesar Ymanuel Epanto |                         |\n| Members:                   | Michael Anthony Vallejo    |                         |\n|                            | Lydie Carylle Leyes        |                         |\n|                            | Catherine BadiHa           | Toni Gorgolon           |\n|                            | Saadodin Pendatun Jr.      | Crystal Weisz De Guzman |\n|                            | Van Carlo Labanan          | Jonathan Israel Gelogo  |\n|                            | Xander Cage Paman          | Johaymen Malawani       |\n|                            |                            |                         |\n\nTasks:'), Document(id='doc_78_chunk_13', metadata={'id': 'doc_78_chunk_13', 'index': 13, 'doc_id': 78}, page_content='Tasks:\n\n- Promote student activities as required by each committee through social networks, posting, other means of promotion/ information dissemination\n- Design the poster, streamer, and tarpaulin\n- Establish and maintains linkages with the outside community in matters relevant to the information dissemination/promotion documentation\n- In charge of answering messages and inquiries regarding the KASAMA Social Media Accounts\n- Release Official Statements of KASAMA on relevant issues and FAQs\n- Ensure activities are posted on the KASAMA Social Media Accounts\n- Ensure that the posts of KASAMA in all social media accounts attain maximum reach.\n\n# **Grievance and Complaints Committee**'), Document(id='doc_78_chunk_14', metadata={'id': 'doc_78_chunk_14', 'index': 14, 'doc_id': 78}, page_content='# **Grievance and Complaints Committee**\n\n| Faculty/Staff Coordinator: | Redeemtor Sacayan     |\n|----------------------------|-----------------------|\n| Chairperson:               | Kyle Christian Tuquib |\n| Co-Chairperson:            | Christine Joy Amper   |\n| Members:                   | Shernan Franz Samson  |\n|                            | Glecie Mae Panes      |\n\nTasks:\n\n- Responsible for resolving matters relating to conflicts, complaints, and/ or grievance of event matters and/ or officer/s and/ or members of the committee against a participant as maybe referred from time to time\n- Implement written policies related to resolving conflicts/complaints\n\n# **Tabulation and Results**\n\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator: Chairperson:\n\nMark Durog Alliah Fayesha Elcamil\n\nInfluencing the Future\n\nCo-Chairperson: Members:'), Document(id='doc_78_chunk_15', metadata={'id': 'doc_78_chunk_15', 'index': 15, 'doc_id': 78}, page_content='# **Tabulation and Results**\n\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator: Chairperson:\n\nMark Durog Alliah Fayesha Elcamil\n\nInfluencing the Future\n\nCo-Chairperson: Members:\n\nThea Cabrera Mohammad Raid Sani Lugille Marien Castardo Credenda Valerie Baja Christille Shyra Norbe Gerald Karl Avila Centerelle Salvaha Mark Ryan L. Uy Reylen Oracion Sarah Jane Nava\n\nErin Joyce Paluga Nicole Asuncion D. Ancheta Joshua Venzon Mavelle Dorothy Serate Rhea Rachel Canoneo Rahmah Naga Azis Alexander Jules Barrete Paulinne Thiesha Baloro Faith Ashley Alidon\n\nTasks:\n\n- Responsible for collection of all the results sheets from the judges after each event\n- Observe confidentiality\n- Manage all tabulation related systems during the entire Palakasan\n- Responsible for all tabulation committee related tasks.\n\n#### **Food Committee**'), Document(id='doc_78_chunk_16', metadata={'id': 'doc_78_chunk_16', 'index': 16, 'doc_id': 78}, page_content='#### **Food Committee**\n\n| Faculty/Staff Coordinator: | Cheryl C. Encabo    |                     |\n|----------------------------|---------------------|---------------------|\n| Chairperson:               | Kimberly Lopez      |                     |\n| Co-Chairperson:            | Mary Twinxer Nuevas |                     |\n| Members:                   | Hernan Garcia       | Keith David Ramayla |\n|                            | Mitchelyn Loresco   |                     |\n\n#### Task:\n\n• Coordinates with appropriate Committees regarding preparation and distribution of snacks and meals for the working committee, judges and sports officials.\n\n#### **Ways and Means**'), Document(id='doc_78_chunk_17', metadata={'id': 'doc_78_chunk_17', 'index': 17, 'doc_id': 78}, page_content='#### Task:\n\n• Coordinates with appropriate Committees regarding preparation and distribution of snacks and meals for the working committee, judges and sports officials.\n\n#### **Ways and Means**\n\n| Faculty/Staff Coordinator: | Suhaydah M. Saripada      |                     |\n|----------------------------|---------------------------|---------------------|\n| Chairperson:               | Aries Espina              |                     |\n| Co-Chairperson:            | Ma. Arvie Faith Escasinas |                     |\n| Members:                   | Micah Real                | Shania Gonzaga      |\n|                            | Ma. Arvie Joyce Escasinas | Nathaniel Palma     |\n|                            | Shane Marie Villoria      | Naim Saad           |\n|                            | Hermione Sansona          | John Paul Villamora |\n|                            | Mary Gwyneth Manlapaz     |                     |\n\n#### Task:'), Document(id='doc_78_chunk_18', metadata={'id': 'doc_78_chunk_18', 'index': 18, 'doc_id': 78}, page_content='#### Task:\n\n• In charge of finding donors, sponsorships, solicitations, and any means that would defray the operational expenses of the whole duration of the event\n\n## **Health, Safety Management Services & Security and Order Committee**\n\n| Faculty/Staff Coordinators: | Peter D. Suson & Hassanor S. Bansao |\n|-----------------------------|-------------------------------------|\n| Chairperson:                | Veanamari Elise Santillan           |\n| Co-Chairperson:             | Hernan Garcia                       |\n| Members:                    | Alyssa T. Heyrana                   |\n|                             | Mariane Therese Ambag               |\n|                             | Recca Marie Azarcon                 |\n\nTasks:\n\n- Responsible for the overall direction of all security functions\n- Observe and report any unlawful or inappropriate activity\n\nwww msuiit edu.ph\n\nInfluencing the Future'), Document(id='doc_78_chunk_19', metadata={'id': 'doc_78_chunk_19', 'index': 19, 'doc_id': 78}, page_content="Tasks:\n\n- Responsible for the overall direction of all security functions\n- Observe and report any unlawful or inappropriate activity\n\nwww msuiit edu.ph\n\nInfluencing the Future\n\n- Provide protection and ensure safety for Individuals and property\n- Manage emergency situations and report to authorities as appropriate\n- Ensures that the University's medical staff and rescue team are prepared to respond to emergencies during all pre-event and during PALAKASAN activities;\n- Assigns medical personnel at the venues for all pre-event and during PALAKASAN activities;\n- Ensures that medical kits are available;\n- Assigns medical personnel at the clinic during all pre-event and during PALAKASAN activities; and\n- To quickly and effectively respond to and recover from disaster\n\n# **Planning and Stage Production Management & Audio and Multimedia System (Technicals) Committee**"), Document(id='doc_78_chunk_20', metadata={'id': 'doc_78_chunk_20', 'index': 20, 'doc_id': 78}, page_content='# **Planning and Stage Production Management & Audio and Multimedia System (Technicals) Committee**\n\n| Faculty/Staff Coordinator: | Rabby Q. Lavilles        |  |\n|-----