78}, page_content='| Faculty/Staff Coordinator:                          | Jay Roel Semilla                                  |                         |\n| Chairperson:                                        | Nichole Simblante                                 |                         |\n| Co-Chairperson:                                     | Art Joseph Tarranza                               |                         |\n| Members:                                            | Lodelyn Prado                                     | Jeff Aquilar            |\n|                                                     | Christian Roy Escolano                            | Allen Dave Capa         |\n|                                                     | Harvey Melendez                                   | Christian Nico Alagcan  |\n|                                                     | Zailla Althea Alarde                              | Kathleen Anne Fumero    |'), Document(id='doc_78_chunk_29', metadata={'id': 'doc_78_chunk_29', 'index': 29, 'doc_id': 78}, page_content='|                                                     | Zailla Althea Alarde                              | Kathleen Anne Fumero    |\n|                                                     | Leo Herold Laluna                                 | Jaimie Calunod          |\n|                                                     | Jayvee Bondoc                                     | Franzyn Maryel Incon    |\n|                                                     | Mark Angelo Gallardo                              | Justinne Rae Felizarta  |\n|                                                     | Ella May Capricho                                 | Devlin Fritz Villanueva |\n|                                                     | Christine Grace Cognito                           | Bryan Alexander Open    |\n|                                                     | Laika Angagao                                     | Zhea Sanchez            |'), Document(id='doc_78_chunk_30', metadata={'id': 'doc_78_chunk_30', 'index': 30, 'doc_id': 78}, page_content='|                                                     | Laika Angagao                                     | Zhea Sanchez            |\n|                                                     | Shane Heart Buhisan                               | Khylle Zed Mag-aso      |'), Document(id='doc_78_chunk_31', metadata={'id': 'doc_78_chunk_31', 'index': 31, 'doc_id': 78}, page_content='Marchell Rose Solana\n\nTristan Jake Segura\n\nElritz Lauron\n\nSitty Hedjarah Guro\n\nJesciller Villaruz Jr.\n\nOFFICE OF THE UNIVERSITY CHANCELLOR MINDANAO STATE UNIVERSITY - ILIGAN INSTITUTE OF TECHNOLOGY\n\nInfluencing the Future\n\n- Faculty/Staff Coordinator: Chairperson: Co-Chairperson: Members:\n- Renebel O. Labadisos Joshua Pinlac Mary Ingrid Bumatay Kimberly Bonete Fatima Myrrh Holy Faith Opog\n- Rochelle Rose Rocha Krizyl Ann Ong Jhon Lloyd Pioquinto\n\n#### Committee for Special Events\n\nwww.msuiit.edu.ph'), Document(id='doc_78_chunk_32', metadata={'id': 'doc_78_chunk_32', 'index': 32, 'doc_id': 78}, page_content='#### Committee for Special Events\n\nwww.msuiit.edu.ph\n\n| Faculty/Staff Coordinator: Jed B. Otano          |                                      |                 |\n|--------------------------------------------------|--------------------------------------|-----------------|\n| Faculty/Staff Co-coordinator: John Leandro Reyes |                                      |                 |\n| Chairperson:                                     | Cherry Mae Tabaña                    |                 |\n| Co-Chairperson:                                  | Alfrem Mogan & Kryzzl Joie Lastimosa |                 |\n| Members:                                         | Kecy Naneth Saliwa                   | Francis Vale    |\n|                                                  | Charles Frederick Tilacas            | Mc PG II Abayan |\n|                                                  | Cris Enterone                        |                 |\n\n#### Committee for Mx. Influencer'), Document(id='doc_78_chunk_33', metadata={'id': 'doc_78_chunk_33', 'index': 33, 'doc_id': 78}, page_content='#### Committee for Mx. Influencer\n\n| Amado C. Guinto Jr.                               |  |\n|---------------------------------------------------|--|\n| Christine Jane Tecson                             |  |\n| Andrianne Nicole Arda                             |  |\n| Meggie Denise Villanueva<br>Irene Canete          |  |\n| Mary Grace Cabalhin<br>Ernest Sabilla             |  |\n| Beatrix Julianna Marie Malacas<br>Janrose Sabuero |  |\n| Cedric Pejan<br>EN Khrisna Carumba                |  |\n| Lynne Jasel Mutia<br>Shekirah Maghinay            |  |\n| Headed by Trixcel Emborong of Trixavaganga        |  |\n| The Tent Studio                                   |  |\n|                                                   |  |\n\n### Committee for MSU-IIT Drag Superstar'), Document(id='doc_78_chunk_34', metadata={'id': 'doc_78_chunk_34', 'index': 34, 'doc_id': 78}, page_content='### Committee for MSU-IIT Drag Superstar\n\n| Faculty/Staff Coordinator: | Daryl O. Porras & Jaypee S. Yongco |                          |\n|----------------------------|------------------------------------|--------------------------|\n| Chairperson:               | Alfrem Mogan                       |                          |\n| Co-Chairperson:            | lan Zandro                         |                          |\n| Members:                   | Nikko Shane Dar                    | Anthony Gerarman         |\n|                            | Hujaype Lomondot                   | Christfer-John Maglasang |\n|                            | Shaina Joy Aban                    | Verneece Charity Amlon   |\n|                            | Mil Opema Agan                     | Joanna Rose Alo          |\n|                            | Sheindyl Ann Jabines               | Dominador Maylon Jr.     |\n\n# Committee for Awards, Prizes, Tokens, and Certificates'), Document(id='doc_78_chunk_35', metadata={'id': 'doc_78_chunk_35', 'index': 35, 'doc_id': 78}, page_content='# Committee for Awards, Prizes, Tokens, and Certificates\n\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator: Chairperson: Co-Chairperson:\n\nKiziah G. Dato Sheika Shaila Aclainie G. Bacolod Hyrah Kaye C. Hallera & Hafzah Imam\n\n# Committee for Lights & Sound, Power, and Ventilation\n\nFaculty/Staff Coordinator: Chairperson: Co-Chairperson:\n\nNoel R. Estoperez Cris Enterone Val Sydrick Abarca\n\nInfluencing the Future\n\nAll committees shall perform other tasks as may be assigned by the overall Chairperson of the activity. The chairperson of each committee shall submit a report to the Steering Committee for consolidation.\n\nIn support of this activity, all students shall be excused from their classes during the period stipulated above. They shall also be allowed entry to the campus during weekends and holidays for rehearsals (until 8:00 p.m.) only, subject to University policies and regulations. Further, the students shall be allowed the use of available University facilities, free of charge, for the 2023 Palakasan.'), Document(id='doc_78_chunk_36', metadata={'id': 'doc_78_chunk_36', 'index': 36, 'doc_id': 78}, page_content='In addition, preliminary games for the Palakasan (Sports and eSports) shall be conducted on March 27, 2023.\n\nAll expenses pertaining to the conduct of the Palakasan shall be charged against the budget allocated for the 2023 Palakasan, subject to existing accounting and auditing rules and regulations.\n\nOvertime fees for janitorial services and technical support shall be provided for services rendered during the duration of the activities, charged against the approved budget allocation for 2023 Palakasan, subject to the usual accounting and auditing rules and regulations.\n\nThis Order is effective on the period stipulated above, unless revoked by competent authority.\n\n**ALIZJ EY M. DITUCALAI** Chancellor')]
