INFO 2025-04-21 07:32:10,976 documents 449 139646323328704 Chunks: [Document(id='doc_72_chunk_0', metadata={'id': 'doc_72_chunk_0', 'index': 0, 'doc_id': 72}, page_content='www.msuiit.edu.ph\n\nOffice of the University Chancellor\nMindanao State University - Iligan Institute of Technology\n\nInfluencing the Future\n\nOctober 9, 2024\n\nMEMORANDUM\n\nTO:\n\nAll Concerned Responsibility Center Heads\nThis University\n\nSUBJECT:\n\nMonitoring and Submission of Report on the Number of Transactions for\nInternal and External Services Availed of by the University’s Clientele\n\nIn cognizance of the Harmonized Client Satisfaction Measurement (CSM) and Anti-Red\nTape Authority Memorandum Circulars 2022-005 and 2023-005, all Responsibility Centers\nproviding internal and external services must record all received, completed, and\npending transactions. This data will be included in the Client Satisfaction Measurement Report\n(CSMR) to be submitted by the University to the Anti-Red Tape Authority every last working day\n\nof April, as required by Section 4.7 of the circular.\n\nSection 3.1.2.3 of ARTA MC No. 2019-002-A defines internal and external services as:'), Document(id='doc_72_chunk_1', metadata={'id': 'doc_72_chunk_1', 'index': 1, 'doc_id': 72}, page_content='of April, as required by Section 4.7 of the circular.\n\nSection 3.1.2.3 of ARTA MC No. 2019-002-A defines internal and external services as:\n\nInternal Services- applied for or requested by citizens or clients who are withinthe\nrespective government agency or office, such as, but not limited to, its personnel or\n\nemployees, whether regular or contractual.\n\nExternal Services- applied for or requested by external citizens or clients or those\nwho do not form part or belong to the government agency or office providing the\n\nservice.\n\nResponsibility Centers are tasked with the monthly monitoring and reporting of the\n\nfollowing data for every internal and external service availed of by clients:\n\n•  Number of internal and external services/transactions availed/received;\n•  Number of internal and external services/transactions facilitated;\n•  Number of internal and external services/transactions completed;\n•  Number of internal and external services/transactions pending (backlogs) as of'), Document(id='doc_72_chunk_2', metadata={'id': 'doc_72_chunk_2', 'index': 2, 'doc_id': 72}, page_content='the reporting date.\n\nThe recording of the number of transactions or services availed of by a client can be\nefficiently managed and done by establishing a tracking system using a spreadsheet or\ndatabase software, or manual, using physical log books or printed forms. The record should\ninclude details such as but not limited to client name, service requested, date of request, and\nstatus of request. The records of transactions or services availed of by clients may be requested\nby Anti-Red Tape Authority (ARTA) personnel during field inspections and validation visits.\n\nTelefax: (063) 221-4056 (DL)\nchancellor@g.msuiit.edu.ph\n\nAndres Bonifacio Avenue,\nTibanga, lligan City, 9200\n\nJ\n\n\x0cwww.msuiit.edu.ph\n\nOffice of the University Chancellor\nMindanao State University - Iligan Institute of Technology\n\nInfluencing the Future'), Document(id='doc_72_chunk_3', metadata={'id': 'doc_72_chunk_3', 'index': 3, 'doc_id': 72}, page_content='Andres Bonifacio Avenue,\nTibanga, lligan City, 9200\n\nJ\n\n\x0cwww.msuiit.edu.ph\n\nOffice of the University Chancellor\nMindanao State University - Iligan Institute of Technology\n\nInfluencing the Future\n\nAll Responsibility Center (RC) Heads shall be accountable for submitting these\nreports to the Office of Monitoring and Evaluation, Office of the Vice-Chancellor for Strategic\nInitiatives, every first working day of the month. The submission should follow the template\nattached to this memorandum.\n\nBelow is the indicative schedule of the submission of the said report:\n\nPeriod Covered\n\nSubmission Schedule/Deadline\n\nJanuary\n\nFebruary\n\nMarch\n\nApril\n\nMay\n\nJune\n\nJuly\n\nAugust\n\nSeptember\n\nOctober\n\nNovember\n\nDecember\n\n1 st working day of February\n\n1 st working day of March\n\n1 st working day of April\n\n1 st working day of May\n\n1 st working day of June\n\n1st working day of July\n\n1 st working day of August\n\n1 st working day of September\n\n1 st working day of October\n\n1 st working day of November'), Document(id='doc_72_chunk_4', metadata={'id': 'doc_72_chunk_4', 'index': 4, 'doc_id': 72}, page_content='1 st working day of May\n\n1 st working day of June\n\n1st working day of July\n\n1 st working day of August\n\n1 st working day of September\n\n1 st working day of October\n\n1 st working day of November\n\n1 st working day of December\n\n1st working day of January\n\nMoreover, RC Heads are requested to submit the report on the Number of\nTransactions for Internal and External Services Availed of by the University’s Clientele for\nNovember 4, 2024, using the\n\nJune, July, August, September, and October 2024 on\nprescribed template.\n\nFor strict compliance.\n\nNEYNI. DITI\nALIZI\nChancellor\n”_r\n\nLAN\n\nTelefax: (063) 221-4056 (DL)\nchancellor@g.msuiit.edu.ph\n\nAndres Bonifacio Avenue.\nTibanga, lligan City, 9200\n\n\x0cwww.msuiit.edu.ph\n\nOffice of the University Chancellor\nMindanao State University - Iligan Institute of Technology\n\nInfluencing the Future\n\n(Office Header)\n\nMonthly Monitoring Report of Internal and External Services\n\nReporting Period (Period Covered): Month:\n\nYear:\n\nResponsibility Center:\n\nReported by:'), Document(id='doc_72_chunk_5', metadata={'id': 'doc_72_chunk_5', 'index': 5, 'doc_id': 72}, page_content='Influencing the Future\n\n(Office Header)\n\nMonthly Monitoring Report of Internal and External Services\n\nReporting Period (Period Covered): Month:\n\nYear:\n\nResponsibility Center:\n\nReported by:\n\n(Name of RC Head/ln-Charqe)\n\nI. Summary of Transaction/Services\n\nInternal Services\n\nName of the Service/Transaction\n\nAvailed/Received\n\nFacilitated\n\nCompleted\n\nNO. OF SERVICES/TRANSACTIONS\n\nInternal Service 1\nInternal Service 2\nInternal Service 3\nInternal Service 4\nInternal Service 5\n\nExternal Services\n\nName of the Service/Transaction\n\nExternal Service 1\nExternal Service 2\nExternal Service 3\nExternal Service 4\nExternal Service 5\n\n________ NO. OF SERVICES/TRANSACTIONS\nAvailed/Received\n\nCompleted\n\nFacilitated\n\nPending\n(Backlogs)\n\nPending\n(Backlogs)\n\nII. Details of Pending (Backlogs) Transactions\n\nPlease provide the details of any pending or backlogged transactions.\n\nClient Name/ID\n\nDate\nAvailed\n\nReason for Pending\nStatus\n\nEstimated\nCompletion\nDate\n\nName of the\nService/T ransaction'), Document(id='doc_72_chunk_6', metadata={'id': 'doc_72_chunk_6', 'index': 6, 'doc_id': 72}, page_content='Please provide the details of any pending or backlogged transactions.\n\nClient Name/ID\n\nDate\nAvailed\n\nReason for Pending\nStatus\n\nEstimated\nCompletion\nDate\n\nName of the\nService/T ransaction\n\nInternal Service 1\nInternal Service 2\nInternal Service 3\nExternal Service 1\nExternal Service 2\n\nIII. Remarks (if any)\n\nService Type\n(Internal or\nExternal)\nInternal\nInternal\nInternal\nExternal\nExternal\n\nAdditional comments or explanations regarding the transactions or any other relevant information.\n\nPrepared by:\n\nReviewed by:\n\nName of In-Charge\nPosition\nDate\n\nName of RC Head\nPosition\nDate\n\n(Office Footer)\n\nTelefax: (063) 221-4056 (DL)\nchancellor@g.msuiit.edu.ph\n\nAndres Bonifacio Avenue,\nTibanga, lligan City, 9200')]
