apha Faculty/Staff Co-Chairperson: Geraldine S. Ridad Members: Leoneva Cawaling\n\nNestor T. Cuevas, Jr.\n\nEllen C. Jarantilla\n\n# **Committee for Basketball Tournament:**\n\n| Faculty/Staff Chairperson: | Josue R. Tagalog      |\n|----------------------------|-----------------------|\n| Members:                   | Erick Gunnar C. Halim |\n|                            |                       |\n\nChiedel Joan G. San Diego\n\nJaypee A. Pedro Rexan E. Villaver Mikhail Don L. Patria\n\nwww.msuiit.edu.ph\n\nOFFICE OF THE UNIVERSITY CHANCELLOR MINDANAO STATE UNIVERSITY - ILIGAN INSTITUTE OF TECHNOLOGY\n\nInfluencing the Future'), Document(id='doc_78_chunk_23', metadata={'id': 'doc_78_chunk_23', 'index': 23, 'doc_id': 78}, page_content='| Committee for Chess Tournament:                     |                                                   |                         |\n|-----------------------------------------------------|---------------------------------------------------|-------------------------|\n| Faculty/Staff Chairperson:                          | Junah L. Nagba                                    |                         |\n| Faculty/Staff Co-Chairperson:                       | Victor Rosales                                    |                         |\n| Members:                                            | Vanessa S. Maghanoy                               | Gianina Bianca B. Opema |\n| Committee for Futsal Men Tournament:                |                                                   |                         |\n| Faculty/Staff Chairperson:                          | Art Brian S. Escabarte                            |                         |'), Document(id='doc_78_chunk_24', metadata={'id': 'doc_78_chunk_24', 'index': 24, 'doc_id': 78}, page_content='| Faculty/Staff Chairperson:                          | Art Brian S. Escabarte                            |                         |\n| Faculty/Staff Co-Chairperson:                       | Lad H. Labrada                                    |                         |\n| Members:                                            | Griffter A. Sumando                               | Juvel L. Ompoc          |\n|                                                     | Angelito V. Britos                                |                         |\n|                                                     |                                                   |                         |\n| Committee for Tennis Tournament:                    |                                                   |                         |\n| Faculty/Staff Chairperson:                          | Jiddo Andrei G. Maranda                           |                         |'), Document(id='doc_78_chunk_25', metadata={'id': 'doc_78_chunk_25', 'index': 25, 'doc_id': 78}, page_content='| Faculty/Staff Chairperson:                          | Jiddo Andrei G. Maranda                           |                         |\n| Faculty/Staff Co-Chairperson:                       | Rambe C. Ramel, Jr.                               |                         |\n| Members:                                            | Carl lan L. Divina                                | Jhonlenon A. Aliser     |\n| Committee for Volleyball Tournament:                |                                                   |                         |\n| Faculty/Staff Chairperson:                          | Eddie G. Toring                                   |                         |\n| Faculty/Staff Co-Chairperson:                       | Lyndie P. Toring                                  |                         |\n| Members:                                            | Jet C. Longakit                                   | Felix M. Aque, Jr.      |'), Document(id='doc_78_chunk_26', metadata={'id': 'doc_78_chunk_26', 'index': 26, 'doc_id': 78}, page_content='| Members:                                            | Jet C. Longakit                    