## MEMORANDUM

| TO | Asst. Prof. Helen R. Betonio |
|----|------------------------------|
|    | Department of English (CASS) |

# SUBJECT

You are designated as Special Disbursing Officer, in addition to your regular duties and responsibilities, without additional compensation.

As such, you are authorized to draw cash advance in the amount of Four Thousand Nine Hundred Ninety Nine pesos (P4,999.00) to defray expenses for the PALAKASAN 2018 Literary Events.

The said expenses shall be chargeable against the Palakasan Fund, subject to the usual accounting and auditing rules and regulations.
