INFO 2025-04-21 10:58:45,294 documents 136 140627362674368 Chunks: [Document(id='doc_7_chunk_0', metadata={'id': 'doc_7_chunk_0', 'index': 0, 'doc_id': 7}, page_content='lligan Address: A.Bonifacio Avenue, Iligan City Telefax- (063) 221-4056 (DL) (063) 492-1173 (Globe) (063) 221-4050 - 55 (TL) Manila Address: MSU-IIT MANILA INFORMATION & LIAISON OFFICE Bldg.4 GSIS Metro Homes GA - 9, Pureza cor. Anonas St., Sta Mesa Manila Tel. (02) 716 - 3875\n\nOctober 17, 2018\n\n## MEMORANDUM\n\n| TO | Asst. Prof. Helen R. Betonio |\n|----|------------------------------|\n|    | Department of English (CASS) |\n\n# SUBJECT\n\nYou are designated as Special Disbursing Officer, in addition to your regular duties and responsibilities, without additional compensation.\n\nAs such, you are authorized to draw cash advance in the amount of Four Thousand Nine Hundred Ninety Nine pesos (P4,999.00) to defray expenses for the PALAKASAN 2018 Literary Events.\n\nThe said expenses shall be chargeable against the Palakasan Fund, subject to the usual accounting and auditing rules and regulations.'), Document(id='doc_7_chunk_1', metadata={'id': 'doc_7_chunk_1', 'index': 1, 'doc_id': 7}, page_content='The said expenses shall be chargeable against the Palakasan Fund, subject to the usual accounting and auditing rules and regulations.\n\nYou are further advised to liquidate said cash advance upon exhaustion before you are granted another one.\n\n> FOR AND IN THE ABSENCE OF THE CHANCELLOR:\n\nFRANCO G. TEVES, Ph.D. Vice Chancellor for Academic Affairs, and Officer-in-Charge 7\n\nlligan Address: A.Bonifacio Avenue, Illigan City Telefax- (063) 221-4056 (DL) (063) 492-1173 (Globe) (063) 221-4050 - 55 (TL) Manila Address: MSU-IIT MANILA INFORMATION & LIAISON OFFICE Bldg.4 GSIS Metro Homes GA - 9, Pureza cor. Anonas St., Sta Mesa Manila Tel. (02) 716 - 3875\n\nOctober 17, 2018\n\n## MEMORANDUM\n\n| TO | Assoc. Prof. Vannie Joy T. Resabal     |\n|----|----------------------------------------|\n|    | Department of Electrical, Electronics, |\n|    | and Computer Engineering (COET)        |\n\n#### SUBJECT : Authority to Draw Cash Advance'), Document(id='doc_7_chunk_2', metadata={'id': 'doc_7_chunk_2', 'index': 2, 'doc_id': 7}, page_content='#### SUBJECT : Authority to Draw Cash Advance\n\nYou are designated as Special Disbursing Officer, in addition to your regular duties and responsibilities, without additional compensation.\n\nAs such, you are authorized to draw cash advance in the amount of Four Thousand Nine Hundred Ninety Nine pesos (P4,999.00) to defray expenses for the PALAKASAN 2018 Literary Events.\n\nThe said expenses shall be chargeable against the Palakasan Fund, subject to the usual accounting and auditing rules and regulations.\n\nYou are further advised to liquidate said cash advance upon exhaustion before you are granted another one.\n\n> FOR AND IN THE ABSENCE OF THE CHANCELLOR:\n\nIn FRANCO G. TEVES, Ph.D. Vice Chancellor for Academic Affairs, and Officer-in-Charge\n\nIligan Address: A.Bonifacio Avenue, Iligan City Telefax- (063) 221-4056 (DL) (063) 492-1173 (Globe) (063) 221-4050 - 55 (TL)'), Document(id='doc_7_chunk_3', metadata={'id': 'doc_7_chunk_3', 'index': 3, 'doc_id': 7}, page_content='Iligan Address: A.Bonifacio Avenue, Iligan City Telefax- (063) 221-4056 (DL) (063) 492-1173 (Globe) (063) 221-4050 - 55 (TL)\n\nManila Address: MSU-IIT MANILA INFORMATION & LIAISON OFFICE Bldg.4 GSIS Metro Homes GA - 9, Pureza cor. Anonas St., Sta Mesa Manila Tel. (02) 716 - 3875\n\nOctober 17, 2018\n\n### MEMORANDUM\n\n|  | Assoc. Prof. Michael Lloyd A. Bation |\n|--|--------------------------------------|\n|  | Department of Accountancy (CBAA)     |\n|  |                                      |\n\nAuthority to Draw Cash Advance SUBJECT :\n\nYou are designated as Special Disbursing Officer, in addition to your regular duties and responsibilities, without additional compensation.\n\nAs such, you are authorized to draw cash advance in the amount of Four Thousand Nine Hundred Ninety Nine pesos (P4,999.00) to defray expenses for the PALAKASAN 2018 Literary Events.\n\nThe said expenses shall be chargeable against the Palakasan Fund, subject to the usual accounting and auditing rules and regulations.'), Document(id='doc_7_chunk_4', metadata={'id': 'doc_7_chunk_4', 'index': 4, 'doc_id': 7}, page_content='The said expenses shall be chargeable against the Palakasan Fund, subject to the usual accounting and auditing rules and regulations.\n\nYou are further advised to liquidate said cash advance upon exhaustion before you are granted another one.\n\n> FOR AND IN THE ABSENCE OF THE CHANCELLOR:\n\nFRANCO G. TEVES, Ph.D. Vice Chancellor for Academic Affairs.\n\nand Officer-in-Charge\n\nlligan Address: A.Bonifacio Avenue, Iligan City Telefax- (063) 221-4056 (DL) (063) 492-1173 (Globe) (063) 221-4050 - 55 (TL)\n\nManila Address: MSU-IIT MANILA INFORMATION & LIAISON OFFICE Bldg.4 GSIS Metro Homes GA - 9, Pureza cor. Anonas St., Sta Mesa Manila Tel. (02) 716 - 3875\n\nOctober 17, 2018\n\n### MEMORANDUM\n\n|  | Asst. Prof. Irish Mae Fernandez-Dalona |\n|--|----------------------------------------|\n|  | Department of English (CASS)           |\n\n#### SUBJECT : Authority to Draw Cash Advance'), Document(id='doc_7_chunk_5', metadata={'id': 'doc_7_chunk_5', 'index': 5, 'doc_id': 7}, page_content='|  | Asst. Prof. Irish Mae Fernandez-Dalona |\n|--|----------------------------------------|\n|  | Department of English (CASS)           |\n\n#### SUBJECT : Authority to Draw Cash Advance\n\nYou are designated as Special Disbursing Officer, in addition to your regular duties and responsibilities, without additional compensation.\n\nAs such, you are authorized to draw cash advance in the amount of Four Thousand Nine Hundred Ninety Nine pesos (P4,999.00) to defray expenses for the PALAKASAN 2018 Literary Events.\n\nThe said expenses shall be chargeable against the Palakasan Fund, subject to the usual accounting and auditing rules and regulations.\n\nYou are further advised to liquidate said cash advance upon exhaustion before you are granted another one.\n\n> FOR AND IN THE ABSENCE OF THE CHANCELLOR:\n\nAnn FRANCO G. TEVES, Ph.D. Vice Chancellor for Academic Affairs, and Officer-in-Charge')]
