INFO 2025-04-21 11:27:40,958 documents 136 140627362674368 Chunks: [Document(id='doc_6_chunk_0', metadata={'id': 'doc_6_chunk_0', 'index': 0, 'doc_id': 6}, page_content='<!-- image -->\n\n## OFFICE OF ThE CHANCELLOR\n\nIligan Address: Telefax- (063) 221-4056 (DL) (063) 492-1173 (Giobe) (053) 221-4050 55 (TL)\n\nManila Address: Bldg.4 GSIS Metro Homes GA - 9 Pureza cor. Anonas St, Sta Mesa Manila Tel. (02) 716 3875\n\nOctober 17,2018\n\n## MEMORANDUM\n\nTO\n\nAsst. Prof. Helen R. Betonio\n\nDepartment of English (CASS)\n\nSUBJECT\n\nAuthority to Draw Cash Advance\n\nYou are designated as Special Disbursing Officer; in addition to your regular duties and responsibilities; without additional compensation.\n\nAs such, you are authorized to draw cash advance in the amount of Four Thousand Nine Hundred Ninety Nine pesos (P4,999.00) to defray expenses for the PALAKASAN 2018 Literary Events.\n\nThe said expenses shall be chargcable against the Palakasan Fund, subject to the usual accounting and auditing rules and regulations.\n\nYou are further advised to liquidate said cash advance upon exhaustion before are granted another one. you\n\nFOR AND IN THE ABSENCE OF THE CHANCELLOR:\n\nFRANCO'), Document(id='doc_6_chunk_1', metadata={'id': 'doc_6_chunk_1', 'index': 1, 'doc_id': 6}, page_content='You are further advised to liquidate said cash advance upon exhaustion before are granted another one. you\n\nFOR AND IN THE ABSENCE OF THE CHANCELLOR:\n\nFRANCO\n\nTEVES, Ph.D\n\nVice Chancellor for Academic Affairs,\n\nand Officcr-in-Charge\n\n<!-- image -->\n\n<!-- image -->\n\n## OFFICE OF ThE CHANCELLOR\n\nIligan Address: Telefax - (063) 221-4056 (DL) (063) 492-1173 {Globe) (063) 221-4050 55 (TL)\n\nManila Address: MSU-IIT MANILA INFORMATION &amp; LIAISON OFFICE Bidg 4 GSIS Metro Homes GA - 9, Pureza cor. Anonas St, Sta Mesa Manila Tel. (02) 716 3875\n\nOctober 17, 2018\n\n## MEMORANDUM\n\nTO\n\nAssoc. Prof. Vannie T. Resabal Joy\n\nDepartment of Electrical, Electronics; and Computer Engineering (COET)\n\nSUBJECT\n\nAuthority to Draw Cash Advance\n\nYou are designated as Special Disbursing Officer; in addition to your regular duties and responsibilities, without additional compensation.'), Document(id='doc_6_chunk_2', metadata={'id': 'doc_6_chunk_2', 'index': 2, 'doc_id': 6}, page_content='SUBJECT\n\nAuthority to Draw Cash Advance\n\nYou are designated as Special Disbursing Officer; in addition to your regular duties and responsibilities, without additional compensation.\n\nAs such; you are authorized to draw cash advance in the amount of Four Thousand Nine Hundred Ninety Nine pesos (P4,999.00) to defray expenses for the PALAKASAN 2018 Literary\n\nThe said expenses shall be chargeable against the Palakasan Fund, subject to the usual accounting and auditing rules and regulations.\n\nYou are further advised to liquidate said cash advance upon exhaustion before you are granted another one.\n\n<!-- image -->\n\nFOR AND IN THE ABSENCE OF THE CHANCELLOR:\n\nFRANCO Vice Chancellor for Academic Affairs, and Officer-in-Charge\n\n<!-- image -->\n\n## OFFICE OF THE CHANCELLOR\n\nIligan Address: ABonifacio Avenue, Iligan City Telefax- (063) 221-4056 (DL) (063) 492-1173 (Globe) (063) 221-4050 55 (TL)'), Document(id='doc_6_chunk_3', metadata={'id': 'doc_6_chunk_3', 'index': 3, 'doc_id': 6}, page_content='<!-- image -->\n\n## OFFICE OF THE CHANCELLOR\n\nIligan Address: ABonifacio Avenue, Iligan City Telefax- (063) 221-4056 (DL) (063) 492-1173 (Globe) (063) 221-4050 55 (TL)\n\nManila Address: MSU-IIT MANILA INFORMATION &amp; LIAISON OFFICE Bldg.4 GSIS Metro Homes GA - 9, Pureza cor. Anonas St, Sta Mesa Manila Tel. (02) 716 3875\n\nOctober 17,2018\n\n## MEMORANDUM\n\nTO\n\nAssoc. Prof. Michael Lloyd A. Bation\n\nDepartment of   Accountancy (CBAA)\n\nSUBJECT\n\nAuthority to Draw Cash Advance\n\nYou are designated as Special Disbursing Officer; in addition to your duties and responsibilities, without additional compensation. regular\n\nAs such, you are authorized to draw cash advance in the amount of Four Thousand Nine Hundred Nincty Nine pesos (P4,999.00) to defray expenses for the PALAKASAN 2018 Litcrary Events .\n\nThe said expenses shall be chargeable against the Palakasan Fund, subject to the usual accounting and auditing rules and regulations.'), Document(id='doc_6_chunk_4', metadata={'id': 'doc_6_chunk_4', 'index': 4, 'doc_id': 6}, page_content='The said expenses shall be chargeable against the Palakasan Fund, subject to the usual accounting and auditing rules and regulations.\n\nYou are further advised to liquidate said cash advance upon exhaustion before you are granted another one.\n\nFOR AND IN THE ABSENCE OF THE CHANCELLOR:\n\n<!-- image -->\n\nFRANCO TEVES, Ph.Dc Vice Chancellor for Academic Affairs , and Officer-in-Charge\n\n<!-- image -->\n\n## OFFICE OF THE CHANCELLOR\n\nIligan Address: ABonifacio Avenue, Iligan Teleíax- (063) 221-4056 (DL) (063) 492-1173 (Globe) 55 (TL) City\n\nManila Address: MSU-IIT MANILA INFORMATION &amp; LIAISON OFFICE Bldg.4 GSIS Metro Homes GA - 9, Pureza cor. Anonas SL, Sta Mesa Manila Tel. (02) 716 3875\n\nOctober 17, 2018\n\n## MEMORANDUM\n\nTO\n\nAsst. Prof. Irish Mae Fernandez-Dalona\n\nDepartment of English (CASS)\n\nSUBJECT\n\nAuthority to Draw Cash Advance\n\nYou are designated as Special Disbursing Officer; in addition to your regular duties and responsibilities; without additional compensation.'), Document(id='doc_6_chunk_5', metadata={'id': 'doc_6_chunk_5', 'index': 5, 'doc_id': 6}, page_content='SUBJECT\n\nAuthority to Draw Cash Advance\n\nYou are designated as Special Disbursing Officer; in addition to your regular duties and responsibilities; without additional compensation.\n\nAs such, you are authorized to draw cash advance in the amount of Four Thousand Nine Hundred Ninety Nine pesos (P4,999.00) to expenses for the PALAKASAN 2018 Literary defray\n\nThe said expenses shall be chargeable against the Palakasan Fund, subject to the usual accounting and auditing rules and regulations.\n\nYou are further advised to liquidate said cash advance upon exhaustion before you are granted another one.\n\nFOR AND IN THE ABSENCE OF THE CHANCELLOR:\n\n<!-- image -->\n\nFRANCO TEVES, Ph.D ,\n\nVice Chancellor for Academic Affairs , and Officcr-in-Charge')]
