## MEMORANDUM

## **All Responsibility Center Heads All Financial Analysts and Assistants** This University TO:

## **Deadline for Submission of Approved Project Procurement Management Plan (PPMP) for FY 2023** SUBJECT:

All Responsibility Centers (RCs) are to submit their respective approved Project Procurement Management Plans (PPMPs) FY 2023 for GAA (Fund 01), Income (Fund 05), and Fiduciary (Fund 05) to the Procurement Management Division (PMD) on or before **October 14, 2022** for consolidation into the Annual Procurement Plan (APP). PPMPs submitted late will not be included in the APP.

PPMPs shall strictly conform to the following:
