# MEMORANDUM

#### TO: **All Concerned Responsibility Center Heads** This University

#### SUBJECT: **Monitoring and Submission of Report on the Number of Transactions for Internal and External Services Availed of by the University's Clientele**

In cognizance of the Harmonized Client Satisfaction Measurement (CSM) and Anti-Red Tape Authority Memorandum Circulars 2022-005 and 2023-005, **all Responsibility Centers providing internal and external services must record all received, completed, and pending transactions.** This data will be included in the Client Satisfaction Measurement Report (CSMR) to be submitted by the University to the Anti-Red Tape Authority every last working day of April, as required by Section 4.7 of the circular.

Section 3.1.2.3 of ARTA MC No. 2019-002-A defines internal and external services as:
