INFO 2025-04-21 12:37:31,240 documents 227 139695967143616 Chunks: [Document(id='doc_10_chunk_0', metadata={'id': 'doc_10_chunk_0', 'index': 0, 'doc_id': 10}, page_content="## OFFICE OF THE CHANCELLOR\n\nRepublic of the Philippines ILIGAN INSTITUTE OF TECHNOLOGY of the Mindanao State University\n\nlligan Address: A. Bonifacio Avenue, 9200 Iligan City Telefax - (063) 221- 4056 (DL) (063) 492-1173 (Globe) (063) 221-4050-55(TL)\n\nManila Address: MSU-IIT MANILA INFORMATION & LIAISON OFFICE Bidg. 4 GSIS Metro Homes\n\nGA-9, Pureza cor Anonas St., Sta. Mesa. Manila Tel. (02) 7163875\n\nAugust 14, 2012\n\nSPECIAL ORDER NO.JUS 4 C IIT Series of 2012\n\n## SUBJECT : Assignment of Faculty Members and Administrative Staff as Tournament Managers/Officials during the 2012 Institute Palakasan\n\nTo insure the success of this year's Palakasan and upon the recommendation of the Chairman of the Sports Committee, the following faculty members and administrative staff are hereby assigned as tournament managers/officials during the Institute Palakasan scheduled on August 27-31, 2012:"), Document(id='doc_10_chunk_1', metadata={'id': 'doc_10_chunk_1', 'index': 1, 'doc_id': 10}, page_content='| 1. Benjamin Migrino   | - Basketball Women     |\n|-----------------------|------------------------|\n| 2. Diosdado Villabona | - Basketball Men       |\n| 3. Alma Aborido       | - Volleyball Women     |\n| 4. Novy Novasquez     | - Volleyball Men       |\n| 5. Jean Achacoso      | - Softball Men & Women |\n| 6. Ramon Ferraris     | - Futsal               |\n| 7. Nicolas Aborido    | - Lawn Tennis          |\n| 8. Joselito Baldonado | - Table Tennis         |\n| 9. Jonathan Bucad     | - Badminton            |\n| 10. Michael Dagohoy   | - Chess                |\n| 11. Viena Libres      | - Sepak Takraw         |\n| 12. Rovie Bucad       | - Sepak Takraw         |\n| 13. Harlene Mae Solis | - Dart                 |\n|                       |                        |\n\nAs tournament managers/officials, they shall perform the following:'), Document(id='doc_10_chunk_2', metadata={'id': 'doc_10_chunk_2', 'index': 2, 'doc_id': 10}, page_content='As tournament managers/officials, they shall perform the following:\n\n- 1. Come up with the guidelines and schedule of games\n- 2. Prepare venue for sports competition\n- 3. Coordinate with all representatives of the different competing units\n- 4. Ensure fair and successful conduct of all sports events\n- 5. Submit final report to steering committee for consolidation\n\nAs such, they shall be entitled to compensatory day-off for serving during weekends and holidays except those who are employed as Lecturer and Job Order status.\n\nThis Order takes effect immediately and shall remain in force until the end of the Institute Palakasan unless revoked by competent authority.\n\n> FOR AND IN THE ABSENCE OF THE CHANCELLOR:\n\nJINKY B. BORNALES, Ph.D. Vice Chancellor for Research and Extension and Officer-In-Charge')]
