INFO 2025-04-21 12:50:32,734 documents 136 139628931704512 Chunks: [Document(id='doc_9_chunk_0', metadata={'id': 'doc_9_chunk_0', 'index': 0, 'doc_id': 9}, page_content="Influencing the Future\n\nOctober 9, 2024\n\n# MEMORANDUM\n\n#### TO: **All Concerned Responsibility Center Heads** This University\n\n#### SUBJECT: **Monitoring and Submission of Report on the Number of Transactions for Internal and External Services Availed of by the University's Clientele**\n\nIn cognizance of the Harmonized Client Satisfaction Measurement (CSM) and Anti-Red Tape Authority Memorandum Circulars 2022-005 and 2023-005, **all Responsibility Centers providing internal and external services must record all received, completed, and pending transactions.** This data will be included in the Client Satisfaction Measurement Report (CSMR) to be submitted by the University to the Anti-Red Tape Authority every last working day of April, as required by Section 4.7 of the circular.\n\nSection 3.1.2.3 of ARTA MC No. 2019-002-A defines internal and external services as:"), Document(id='doc_9_chunk_1', metadata={'id': 'doc_9_chunk_1', 'index': 1, 'doc_id': 9}, page_content='Section 3.1.2.3 of ARTA MC No. 2019-002-A defines internal and external services as:\n\n*Internal Services-* applied for or requested by citizens or clients who are *withinthe* respective government agency or office, such as, but not limited to, its personnel or employees, whether regular or contractual.\n\n*External Services-* applied for or *requested by external citizens or clients* or those who *do not form part* or belong to the government agency or office providing the service.\n\nResponsibility Centers are tasked with the monthly monitoring and reporting of the following data for every internal and external service availed of by clients:\n\n- Number of internal and external services/transactions **availed/received;**\n- Number of internal and external services/transactions **facilitated;**\n- Number of internal and external services/transactions **completed;**\n- Number of internal and external services/transactions **pending (backlogs) as of the reporting date.**'), Document(id='doc_9_chunk_2', metadata={'id': 'doc_9_chunk_2', 'index': 2, 'doc_id': 9}, page_content='The recording of the number of transactions or services availed of by a client can be efficiently managed and done by establishing a tracking system using a spreadsheet or database software, or manual, using physical log books or printed forms. The record should include details such as but not limited to client name, service requested, date of request, and status of request. The records of transactions or services availed of by clients may be requested by Anti-Red Tape Authority (ARTA) personnel during field inspections and validation visits.\n\nAndres Bonifacio Avenue, Tibanga, lligan City, 9200\n\n**J**\n\nInfluencing the Future\n\nAll Responsibility Center (RC) Heads **shall be accountable for submitting these reports** to the Office of Monitoring and Evaluation, Office of the Vice-Chancellor for Strategic Initiatives, **every first working day of the month.** The submission should follow the template attached to this memorandum.'), Document(id='doc_9_chunk_3', metadata={'id': 'doc_9_chunk_3', 'index': 3, 'doc_id': 9}, page_content='**Period Covered Submission Schedule/Deadline** January <sup>1</sup> st working day of February February <sup>1</sup> st working day of March March <sup>1</sup> st working day of April April <sup>1</sup> st working day of May May <sup>1</sup> st working day of June June 1st working day of July July <sup>1</sup> st working day of August August <sup>1</sup> st working day of September September <sup>1</sup> st working day of October October <sup>1</sup> st working day of November November <sup>1</sup> st working day of December\n\nBelow is the indicative schedule of the submission of the said report:\n\n**November 4, 2024,** using the Moreover, RC Heads are requested to submit the **report** on the **Number of Transactions for Internal and External Services Availed of by the University\'s Clientele** for **June, July, August, September, and October 2024** on prescribed template.\n\nDecember 1st working day of January\n\nFor strict compliance.\n\n**ALIZI LAN** Chancellor **NEYNI. DITI** "\\_r'), Document(id='doc_9_chunk_4', metadata={'id': 'doc_9_chunk_4', 'index': 4, 'doc_id': 9}, page_content='December 1st working day of January\n\nFor strict compliance.\n\n**ALIZI LAN** Chancellor **NEYNI. DITI** "\\_r\n\nAndres Bonifacio Avenue. Tibanga, lligan City, 9200\n\nTelefax: (063) 221-4056 (DL) [chancellor@g.](mailto:chancellor@g.msuiit.edu.ph)msuiit.edu.ph\n\nInfluencing the Future\n\n*(Office Header)*\n\n# Monthly Monitoring Report of Internal and External Services\n\nReporting Period (Period Covered): Month: Year:\n\nResponsibility Center:\n\nReported by: *(Name ofRC Head/ln-Charqe)*\n\n## I. Summary ofTransaction/Services\n\n### *Internal Services*'), Document(id='doc_9_chunk_5', metadata={'id': 'doc_9_chunk_5', 'index': 5, 'doc_id': 9}, page_content='### *Internal Services*\n\n|                                | NO. OF SERVICES/TRANSACTIONS |             |           |                       |  |\n|--------------------------------|------------------------------|-------------|-----------|-----------------------|--|\n| Name ofthe Service/Transaction | Availed/Received             | Facilitated | Completed | Pending<br>(Backlogs) |  |\n| Internal Service 1             |                              |             |           |                       |  |\n| Internal Service 2             |                              |             |           |                       |  |\n| Internal Service 3             |                              |             |           |                       |  |\n| Internal Service 4             |                              |             |           |                       |  |\n| Internal Service 5             |                              |             |           |                       |  |'), Document(id='doc_9_chunk_6', metadata={'id': 'doc_9_chunk_6', 'index': 6, 'doc_id': 9}, page_content='### *External Services*'), Document(id='doc_9_chunk_7', metadata={'id': 'doc_9_chunk_7', 'index': 7, 'doc_id': 9}, page_content='|                                | ________ NO. OF SERVICES/TRANSACTIONS |             |           |                       |  |  |\n|--------------------------------|---------------------------------------|-------------|-----------|-----------------------|--|--|\n| Name ofthe Service/Transaction | Availed/Received                      | Facilitated | Completed | Pending<br>(Backlogs) |  |  |\n| External Service 1             |                                       |             |           |                       |  |  |\n| External Service 2             |                                       |             |           |                       |  |  |\n| External Service 3             |                                       |             |           |                       |  |  |\n| External Service 4             |                                       |             |           |                       |  |  |'), Document(id='doc_9_chunk_8', metadata={'id': 'doc_9_chunk_8', 'index': 8, 'doc_id': 9}, page_content='| External Service 4             |                                       |             |           |                       |  |  |\n| External Service 5             |                                       |             |           |                       |  |  |'), Document(id='doc_9_chunk_9', metadata={'id': 'doc_9_chunk_9', 'index': 9, 'doc_id': 9}, page_content='## II. Details of Pending (Backlogs) Transactions\n\n*Please provide the details ofany pending orbacklogged transactions.*'), Document(id='doc_9_chunk_10', metadata={'id': 'doc_9_chunk_10', 'index': 10, 'doc_id': 9}, page_content='| Name ofthe<br>Service/Transaction | Service Type<br>(Internalor<br>External) | Client Name/ID | Date<br>Availed | Reason forPending<br>Status | Estimated<br>Completion<br>Date |\n|-----------------------------------|------------------------------------------|----------------|-----------------|-----------------------------|---------------------------------|\n| Internal Service 1                | Internal                                 |                |                 |                             |                                 |\n| Internal Service 2                | Internal                                 |                |                 |                             |                                 |\n| Internal Service 3                | Internal                                 |                |                 |                             |                                 |'), Document(id='doc_9_chunk_11', metadata={'id': 'doc_9_chunk_11', 'index': 11, 'doc_id': 9}, page_content='| Internal Service 3                | Internal                                 |                |                 |                             |                                 |\n| External Service 1                | External                                 |                |                 |                             |                                 |\n| External Service 2                | External                                 |                |                 |                             |                                 |'), Document(id='doc_9_chunk_12', metadata={'id': 'doc_9_chunk_12', 'index': 12, 'doc_id': 9}, page_content='# III. Remarks (if any)\n\n*Additional comments or explanations regarding the transactions or any otherrelevant information.*\n\nPrepared by: Reviewed by:\n\nName of In-Charge Position Date\n\nName of RC Head Position Date\n\n*(Office Footer)*\n\nAndres Bonifacio Avenue, Tibanga, lligan City, 9200')]
